About the Hardware

The hardware consists of SAM4S microcontroller, servo motors, PIR motion sensor and AMW004 Zentri Chip. The flowchart explains the different stages the system runs in when motion is detected. The webcam board was modified from the previous quarte to include the PIR senor and servo
